easy on you or make a particular project really valuable for your team, right? So thinking

00:15:41.719 --> 00:15:47.159
about that as a way to determine what's effortful and what's valuable.

00:15:47.159 --> 00:15:51.599
And then finally, this has been a very data-like talk for a data science conference, but here

