can use that to calibrate and go back over time in this iterative exercise to determine,

00:16:06.119 --> 00:16:09.679
were you right? Have you accurately predicted how effortful and valuable something will

00:16:09.679 --> 00:16:14.559
be? And where you're off, you can tweak. You can adjust how you're doing this to make yourself

00:16:14.559 --> 00:16:16.039
better at it.

